.PP
.\"O The locale for category
.\"O .BI LC_ foo
.\"O is specified by examining the three environment variables
.\"O .BR LC_ALL ,
.\"O .BR LC_\fIfoo\fP ,
.\"O .BR LANG ,
.\"O in that order.
